zen gets out of your way and
makes it easy to get stuff done
-------------------------------

zen is
  a coding agent manager
  a powerful efficient TUI
  ~20 files of safe Rust

zen isnt
  bloatware or spyware
  going to slow you down  
  overselling itself

curl -fsSL https://github.com/TheHiddenLayer/zen/releases/latest/download/zen-$(uname -m | sed 's/arm64/aarch64/')-$(case "$(uname -s)" in Linux) echo "unknown-linux-gnu";; Darwin) echo "apple-darwin";; esac).tar.gz | tar -xz && sudo mv zen /usr/local/bin/
